#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:2
msgid "类"
msgstr "Classes"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:5
msgid "生命周期"
msgstr "Lifecycle"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:6
msgid ""
"整体来说，Java中类的生命周期如下：加载 (Loading) -> [ 连接 (Linking) : 验证 (Verification) -> "
"准备 (Perparation) -> 解析 (Resolutin) ] -> 初始化 (Initialization) -> 使用 "
"(Using) -> 卸载 (Unloading) 。"
msgstr ""
"Overall, the lifecycle of a Java class is as follows: Loading -> [ Linking: "
"Verification -> Preparation -> Resolution ] -> Initialization -> Using -> "
"Unloading."

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:8
msgid "加载过程分为三步："
msgstr "The loading process is divided into three steps:"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:10
msgid "通过全限定类名来获取定义此类的二进制字节流"
msgstr "Obtain the binary byte stream that defines the class by its fully qualified class name"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:11
msgid "将字节流所代表的静态存储结构转化为方法区的运行时数据结构"
msgstr "Convert the static storage structure represented by the byte stream into a runtime data structure in the method area"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:12
msgid "在内存中生成代表这个类的 ``java.lang.Class`` 对象，作为方法区这个类的各种数据的访问入口"
msgstr "Generate a ``java.lang.Class`` object in memory to represent this class, serving as the access entry for the class's data in the method area"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:14
msgid "验证阶段主要用于确保 Class 文件的字节流符合当前虚拟机的要求，分为几步："
msgstr "The verification phase mainly ensures that the byte stream of the Class file meets the requirements of the current virtual machine. It is divided into several steps:"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:16
msgid "判断文件格式：是否以 ``0xCAFEBABE`` 开始，主次版本号是否在处理范围内"
msgstr "Check the file format: whether it starts with ``0xCAFEBABE`` and whether the major and minor version numbers are within the supported range"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:17
msgid "元数据验证"
msgstr "Metadata verification"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:18
msgid "字节码验证"
msgstr "Bytecode verification"

#: ../../source/language/java/class.rst:19
msgid "符号引用验证"
msgstr "Symbolic reference verification"
